<img src="https://cdn.dbusiness.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/33/2020/08/Mercy-Education-Project.jpg" width = "300" height = "200" alt= "Flint Michigan" 
<h3><Center><b>Learn More</b></h3>
<body text="#00FFFD"
<table><center>
<table border=1>
<td><font size=4>	A project that we encourage everyone to look into is the Mercy Education Project because of all the good things they are doing for our community. Their mission is to promote access to opportunities for women and girls in Detroit. They aid women and girls who are less fortunate in Detroit and they really focus on southwest Detroit. They offer many programs such as an after school tutoring for reading and a college and career readiness for 11th and 12th graders. We are super drawn to this project because they support everything we support. They are passionate about helping women grow in all aspects of their lives. The biggest thing we liked about the project is that they do not care about the womens’ economic situation, their beliefs or their backgrounds. It would mean a lot to us if you could donate to this cause and help the women of detroit. You can find them at http://www.mercyed.net or you can call 313-963-5881 to support today!
 </td>
</section>
